data.description: GREAT CURB APPEAL! LARGE, FULLY FENCED BACKYARD!  WELCOME to this meticulously maintained 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, Cape Coral Home boasting over 1500 square feet of living and entertaining space on an almost ¼ acre Lot. The fenced in backyard is large enough for a pool or other outdoor entertainment features – whichever you desire. There is NO carpet in this home – tile flooring throughout to include all 3 bedrooms. The Kitchen and both Bathrooms have been updated and remodeled. The Kitchen features a Counter-Height Island, Granite Countertops, newer Appliances, and Double Bowl Stainless Steel Sink. Both Bathrooms feature Granite Countertops and Tile Shower Walls. The Primary Bedroom has a large closet and ensuite bathroom with walk-in shower. Custom Plantation Shutters adorn a majority of the windows in this home. The addition provides space for both a Dining Room and Living/Sitting Room area. Double Sliding Glass Doors off of both the Living/Sitting Room and Primary Bedroom provide access to the Covered and Screened-in Lanai Patio and backyard. The Roof was replaced in 2020, and the Water Treatment System was replaced in 2022. Conveniently located with close proximity to Great Shopping, Restaurants, Entertainment, and Schools. A MUST SEE Home! Call TODAY for your private showing! You may also View this Matterport 3D Video Link for an immediate Virtual Tour and Showing from the comfort of your current home --- https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=gU9a3WY6nXZ&brand=0&mls=1&
